settings.description: Based on an old little timmy SMF level I did back in 2018: https://drive.google.com/file/d/19mwEvhbKmhqDd_4NnXw_xJ_kea7TUIP-/view

Fly, slide and spin through the sky and Bowser's castle!
(For Smaghetti Build Contest #2.)
Wendy gets her Airship redesigned, With various Airships added for assistant, Mario goes to the airship by using an mini airship instead of climbing, Good Luck Defeating Wendy & Finding a Secret Exit

A remake of Super Mario World 1-1. Somehow, Rexes are now red and hopping. Banzai Bills are now smaller and homes in to you.
[Revision 2: Backtracking from room 2 disabled due to graphical glitches]
Embarking a Journey on the First Unused level but It's Improved by a little bit, Good luck finding the hidden Ace coins!

First level! This is the first of what will be a 72 (plus 1 extra for those who complete all 72 levels 100%!) level series! This will take a while! Good luck getting all 360 Ace coins!
Difficulty: 3/5
